oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Eddie Cummings Job No. 36540
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 1092) for an order placed by Eddie Cummings for 250 window cards and 10 jumbos (three sheets) for a performance by the San Francisco Ballet at the Opry House on March 17. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
